Ward {5}
[i]Misericorde[/i] – Whenever a nontoken creature dies, that creatures controller loses 1 life and draws a card.
[i]Corruption[/i] – {3}, Exile target creature card from a graveyard: Create a X/X black [/i][i]Corrupted[/i][i] creature token, where X is the mana value of the exiled card.
